author: natasha taylor
title: natasha taylor
text:
Very pleased as usual with my purchase of blind. This is the Forth blind I have bought , they are very well made with easy instruction .Easy to order just popped in measurements given an instant Quote: then gave payment.
Good up dates given of when the order will arrive.
Really good quality.
I found this company via Google after using hilarys blinds at my previous home.
The blinds from blinds to go are for better quality and are a better price.
